<article>
  <h2>Articles</h2>
  <blockquote>
    “A vacation is having nothing to do and all day to do it in.”
    <footer>
      <cite>— Robert Orben</cite>
    </footer>
  </blockquote>
  <p>
    Vacations are important for overall well-being, providing a break from routine, reducing stress, and improving physical and mental health.
  </p>
  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th scope="col">Title</th>
        <th scope="col">Link</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      {{range .Articles}}
        <tr>
          <td>{{.Title}}</td>
          <td><a hx-get="/article/{{.Slug}}" hx-target="#main" hx-push-url="true">Read</a></td>
        </tr>
      {{end}}
    </tbody>
  </table>
</article>

